<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.5.9">
<l>māyōn tīya valavalaip perumā vañcap pēyvīya</l>
<l>tūya kuḻavi yāyviṭappā lamutā vamutu ceytiṭṭa</l>
<l>māyaṉ vāṉōr taṉittalaivaṉ malarāṇ mainta ṉevvuyirkkun</l>
<l>tāyōṉ ṟammā ṉeṉṉammā ṉammā mūrtti yaiccārntē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We won’t perish,</l>
<l>reaching that great/dark form of my lord, the lord who expanded</l>
<l>for all living beings, the husband of her on the blossom, the sole leader of the celestials, the trickster</l>
<l>who made ambrosia, the ambrosia being the milk when emitted by the mother of the pure calf,</l>
	<l>while the big dark treacherous demoness of evil confusion perished.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
